{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"touchstart","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element/touchstart_event","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>O evento touchstart</code> é acionado quando o ponteiro de toque<em>(dedo ou caneta)</em> é aplicado sobre à superfície de toque da tela<em>(toque sobre a tela no elemento alvo)</em>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"info_geral","title":"Info Geral","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"especificações\">Especificações</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://w3c.github.io/touch-events/#event-touchstart\" rel=\" noopener\">Touch Events</a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"interface\">Interface</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TouchEvent\"><code>TouchEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"bubbles\">Bubbles</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Sim</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"cancelável\">Cancelável</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Sim</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"alvo\">Alvo</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Documento, Elemento</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"ação_padrão\">Ação Padrão</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">undefined (indefinido)</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>EventTarget</td>\n   <td>The event target (the topmost target in the DOM tree).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>DOMString</td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>Boolean</td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>Boolean</td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>view</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>WindowProxy</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/defaultView\" title=\"In browsers, document.defaultView returns the window object associated with a document, or null if none is available.\"><code>document.defaultView</code></a> (<code>window</code> of the document)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>detail</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>long (float)</td>\n   <td>0.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>touches</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>TouchList</td>\n   <td>A list of <a href=\"/en-US/DOM/Touch\"><code>Touch</code></a>es for every point of contact currently touching the surface.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>targetTouches</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>TouchList</td>\n   <td>A list of <a href=\"/en-US/DOM/Touch\"><code>Touch</code></a>es for every point of contact that is touching the surface and started on the element that is the target of the current event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>changedTouches</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>TouchList</td>\n   <td>A list of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Touch\"><code>Touch</code></a>es for every point of contact which contributed to the event.<br>\n    For the touchstart event this must be a list of the touch points that just became active with the current event. For the touchmove event this must be a list of the touch points that have moved since the last event. For the touchend and touchcancel events this must be a list of the touch points that have just been removed from the surface.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>ctrlKey</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the control key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>shiftKey</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the shift key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>altKey</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the alt key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>metaKey</code> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the meta key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Os códigos de exemplos para este evento estão disponíveis nesta página dedicada: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Touch_events\">Touch events</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span>Característica</span></span></th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>22.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/18\" title=\"Released on 2013-01-08.\">18.0</a> (18.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"pt\"><span>Característica</span></span></th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Chrome para Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Firefox OS</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>6.0 (6.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>11</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eventos_relacionados","title":"Eventos Relacionados","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/touchstart_event\"><code>ontouchstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Info Geral","id":"info_geral"},{"text":"Propriedades","id":"propriedades"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Eventos Relacionados","id":"eventos_relacionados"}],"summary":"O evento touchstart é acionado quando o ponteiro de toque(dedo ou caneta) é aplicado sobre à superfície de toque da tela(toque sobre a tela no elemento alvo).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Element: touchstart event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.ontouchstart","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Element: touchstart イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.ontouchstart","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"touchstart","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/element/touchstart_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/element/touchstart_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element/touchstart_event","title":"touchstart"}],"pageTitle":"touchstart - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}